  • public class RejectionDispatcherRegistry
extends OutputDispatcherRegistry<io.spine.core.RejectionClass,RejectionDispatcher<?>>
    The registry of objects dispatching the rejections to their subscribers.

    There can be multiple dispatchers per rejection class.
